 service or repair
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf1\insrsid12197632 When equipment requires servicing or repair, documentation should
\par accompany the equipment stating if the item has or has not been
\par decontaminated (see Appendix 1).\line 
